snippet.title: StarTrek: Legends - Official Story Trailer
snippet.description:
Star Trek: Legends is coming to Nintendo Switch, PlayStation, and Xbox!

Embark on a legendary journey across the stars with over 70 iconic Star Trek characters at your command. Assemble your dream crew, engage in tactical, turn-based battles, and shape your unique path through the Star Trek universe. With rich storytelling, strategic combat, and immersive missions, Star Trek: Legends brings the thrill of exploration and discovery straight to your console.
Are you ready to take command? The final frontier awaits.
